return ['messages'=>['/high-jewellery/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6/','<p>A tribute of resilience and perseverance, the Lifeboat diamond pendant, crafted from the finest 18K yellow gold, reminds us of our brightest tomorrows amidst a sea of possibilities. It embarks on a journey of adventures and gives us a spirit of endurance for whatever challenges in life.</p>'=>'<p>這款救生艇鑽石墜飾是對韌性和堅持的致敬。採用最優質的18K黃金製作，提醒我們在無限可能的海洋中堅持追求光明的明天。它象徵著冒險的旅程，賦予我們面對各種挑戰的堅韌精神。 </p>','<p>At the heart sits a striking sailboat glistening in silvery brilliance, every jewellery piece of the <em>Splendid Voyage</em> is artfully crafted to pursue and experience the beauty of life, ready to voyage and embark on a journey of imagination. Exploring our extraordinary selections, from the exquisite diamond arm rings to the minimalist geometric brooches and designer necklaces, each piece is designed to be disassembled and transformed into exquisite diamond jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>在心中坐落著一艘閃耀光輝的帆船 — <em>璀璨之航</em>系列每一件珠寶作品都經精心打造，旨在追求與體驗生活的美好，隨時準備啟航，展開一段想像之旅。<br>探索我們這非凡系列，從精美的鑽石臂環，到極簡幾何胸針和設計項鍊，每件作品均可拆卸，並轉化為精緻的鑽石珠寶。 </p>','<p>Crafted with 18K yellow gold and diamonds, these geometric sail brooches capture minimalist elegance with sharp and linear designs. Sleek and sophisticated, these brooches bring a subtle touch of glamorousness, navigating the sailboat on the open sea.</p>'=>'<p>以18K黃金和鑽石精心製作的幾何帆船胸針，以尖銳線條設計捕捉了極簡主義的優雅，流暢而精緻。這胸針為您的造型增添了一絲微妙的奢華感，猶如在開闊的海洋上駛向遠方的帆船。 </p>','<p>Featuring an anchor motif – a signature nautical inspiration of strength, hope and stability, these anchors can be transformed into a pair of extraordinary earrings precisely crafted with gold and diamonds.</p>'=>'<p>這對耳環以錨為主題，象徵力量、希望與穩定，黃金和鑽石巧妙融合，展現獨特的航海靈感。</p>','<p>Setting out into the vast ocean with nothing but the wind, the waves and the sails is a fun and thrilling adventure like no other. Fueling with passion for sailing, these exquisite diamond arm rings shimmering in two different patterns, intricate sophisticated craftsmanship and textures – allowing you to set sail in artistic styles.</p>'=>'<p>踏上廣闊的海洋，唯有風、浪和帆——這是一場獨特而激動人心的冒險。這些精美的鑽石臂環以兩種圖案閃耀，展現出精緻而複雜的工藝與質感，讓您優雅啟航。 </p>','<p>The sea, once it casts its spell, holds one in its net of wonder forever. The vastness and beauty of the sea have always been a source of inspiration. There’s nothing quite like sailing on the open sea. The best part of our Splendid Voyage is – the infinite imagination always reminds us that possibility awaits in life. From brilliant diamonds to the unique nautical-inspired designs, each piece of jewellery showcases exceptional artistry and ingenious style, yearning for adventure and determination to forge ahead.</p><p>Having been dazzled by our Splendid Voyage collection, we dream big dreams! At EJI, our imagination and creativity run wild. We remain dedicated to bringing our passion and pursuit in excellence and craftsmanship to life. We’re all ears and ready to help you create one-of-a-kind piece with our bespoke jewellery service – make your big dreams come true!</p>'=>'<p>海洋的廣闊與美麗始終是靈感的源泉，沒什麼比海上航行更令人陶醉。壯麗航程最美好的部分在於——無盡想像力總是提醒著我們，生活充滿了可能性。    </p><p>從璀璨鑽石，到獨特的航海靈感設計，每一件珠寶都展現了卓越的藝術性和巧妙風格，渴望冒險並堅定向前。在EJI，我們致力發揮想像力和創造力，將我們對卓越工藝的追求化為現實。我們隨時傾聽，助您創造獨一無二的珠寶，讓您夢想成真。   </p>','<p>This splendid nautical burgee pendant draws inspiration from the essence of maritime traditions. It is meticulously crafted with shimmering diamonds – bringing a touch of elegance to the sailboat and evoking the twinkling reflections dancing on the surface of the rough sea.</p>'=>'<p>這華麗的航海旗吊墜融合了海洋的精髓，以閃耀鑽石製作，為帆船增添優雅，喚起在波濤洶湧的海面上跳動的閃爍倒影。 </p>','Anchor Earrings'=>'錨形耳環','GEOMETRIC SAIL BROOCHES​​'=>'幾何帆船胸針','High Jewellery'=>'高級珠寶','Home'=>'首頁','Jewel Treasure I'=>'珠寶珍寶 I','Jewel Treasure II'=>'珠寶珍寶 II','Jewel Treasure III'=>'珠寶珍寶 III','Jewel Treasure IV'=>'珠寶珍寶 IV','Jewel Treasure V'=>'珠寶珍寶 V','Lifeboat Pendant'=>'救生艇吊墜','Nautical Burgee Pendant'=>'航海旗吊墜','Sail Arm Rings'=>'帆船臂環','Set sail and embark on your adventur